  "shortDescription": "Control GitHub faster with a secure desktop app for commits, branches, pull requests, issues, and automated Git workflows.",
  "description": "⚠️ Git must be installed on your system .\nGit Automation Pro is a secure and modern desktop tool that helps developers manage Git and GitHub faster, without repeating command-line tasks.\nConnect your GitHub account, load repositories automatically, clone projects, review changes, commit, push, manage branches, create pull requests, track issues, and run ready-made workflows from one clean interface.\nWith Safe Mode, Dry Run previews, secure token storage, activity logs, and background execution, Git Automation Pro gives you more control, fewer mistakes, and a smoother development workflow.",
